s per learner Data from education analytics group Gradesmatch shows that Gauteng was the province with the most distinctions per learner (0.43). This was followed by KZN (0.42) and the Eastern Cape (0.31). Eden College in Durban was named as the school with the most distinctions per learner (3.97) followed by Herschel Girls in Cape Town (3.92) and Beth Jacobs Girls’ school in Yeoville. Below are the 10 schools with the most distinctions per learners, according to Gradesmatch. Read: Matric 2019: Real pass rate is 38.9% 